text: Kamianets-Podilskyi (; ; ) is a city in Khmelnytskyi Oblast (province), Ukraine. It is the administrative centre of Kamianets-Podilskyi Raion (district). In 2022, 96,896 people lived there. Kamianets-Podilskyi is on the Smotrych River. It is in the Podolia region. Category:Cities in Ukraine Category:Khmelnytskyi Oblast
title: Kamianets-Podilskyi
